descriptions.direction: Located in Kuramathi Island, Kuramathi Maldives is on a private beach. Nika Island Resort & Spa and Holi Faru Dive Site are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Rasdhoo Reef Dive Site and Adivaru Thila Dive Site. With windsurfing, boat tours, and fishing nearby, you'll find plenty of adventures in the water.
descriptions.general: Experience an abundance of unparalleled facilities and features at Kuramathi Maldives.Maintain seamless communication using the complimentary Wi-Fi at resort. Effortlessly arrange transportation to and from the airport using the resort's airport transfer services.Discovering Maldive Islands becomes even more accessible, thanks to the shuttle amenities provided at the resort. For visitors traveling by automobile, complimentary parking is available.During your stay at this fantastic resort, the attentive front desk personnel can provide you with a range of amenities such as luggage storage and safety deposit boxes.Obtaining passes for the town's top entertainments becomes effortless with resort's tours.At the resort, utilize the on-site dry cleaning service and laundry service to maintain your beloved travel attire fresh, allowing you to bring fewer clothes. During leisurely days and evenings, on-site amenities such as daily housekeeping enable you to fully enjoy your accommodation.For visitors wishing to smoke, designated smoking zones can be found. At Kuramathi Maldives, every guestroom is provided with convenient amenities and fittings to ensure a comfortable stay.Enhance your experience at resort with the knowledge that certain rooms are equipped with linen service and air conditioning for your convenience. A few accommodations within Kuramathi Maldives offer unique design elements such as a balcony or terrace. Certain rooms offer in-room amusement features such as the television for your enjoyment.In select rooms within the resort, a refrigerator, a coffee or tea maker, bottled water, instant coffee, instant tea and mini bar is available to cater to your requirements when desired.It is worth noting that certain guest bathrooms feature a hair dryer, toiletries and bathrobes for your convenience. Begin your day carefree at Kuramathi Maldives, as complimentary breakfast is offered for your convenience. Begin your day feeling refreshed and invigorated as you enjoy a delightful cup of quality coffee available at the cafe situated within the resort.At the resort, an assortment of easily accessible and delicious meal choices are available to satisfy your appetite whenever it strikes.At Kuramathi Maldives, they are committed to catering to your unique requirements. They offer a variety of meal choices, encompassing halal alternatives for those with special dietary preferences.Create unforgettable moments with your fellow voyagers just steps away, at resort's karaoke rooms, bar and nightclub, for a delightful evening together.At the resort, discerning guests can also enjoy on-site culinary facilities like BBQ facilities tailored to their preferences.During your stay at resort, an array of engaging activities and amenities guarantees a delightful experience. During your stay, don't forget to allocate some moments to experience the readily available shoreline. Conclude your holiday perfectly with a visit to massage, hot tub, salon, steam room, spa and sauna on your final days. Be sure to drop by the pool at resort at least once during your stay.At Kuramathi Maldives, utmost care is taken to ensure guests' comfort. Relish your preferred beverage in your swimwear by the resort's poolside bar. Discover the fitness amenities at resort to maintain your health and strength during your getaway.
